I would say wrong section, but…you seem a bit distressed already so I will just throw it on the backburner. I do understand your pain, the last few days the help sections have seemed to be like ‘no-help sections’.
Unfortunately for you, I know nothing when it comes to client-sided so it would be the blind leading the blind. I just read your post and the only thing I could ask you that may help you find what is wrong, is if you have have checked the lines that the cmd is showing you.
Stream.java - line 153
RSInterface.java - line 239
etc…

2a62r78.jpg1024×768

Also, an OutOfBoundsException usually means something is missing or unreachable.
Sorry I couldn’t be of much help. Hope somebody who knows what they are doing can give some advice. Good luck.
